    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The prevailing and distinctive spirit or character, as of a person, place, time or group. Can also refer to a prevailing taste or sentiment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
